description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              Your responsibilities

              Accounting duties

              - 	Liaise with bank and authorities;

              - 	Weekly, monthly cash flow management reporting;

              - 	Responsible for VAT, PIT, CIT and FCT submission;

              - 	Handle ad-hoc reports.


              HR duties

              - 	Monthly payroll;

              - 	Liaise with Labor department, Social Insurance authorities;

              - 	Application, Renewal, Issuance  of work permit for foreigner workers;

              - 	Issue relevant letters to staff for labor contract, appointment, confirmation, increment, etc…

              - 	Posting job advertisement, shortlisting and conducting interviews.


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              Your profile

              •	2+ year for full set of accounting and HR experience;

              •	Posesses an analytical mind and good in problem solving;

              •	Team player, with strong interpersonal skills, good communication skills and contribute to a good work environment.


              Interest candidate please send most updated CV together with following information:

              •	Current and expected salary;

              •	Availability;

              •	Reason for leaving previous job.


